commit.message:
Update README.md

Added in guidance on the local usage tool.
Adding local usage tool for testing with direct user input

Create LocalUsage

When run in the same directory as the info_MP_unified.json, runs a local script allowing direct user entry of a constituency, returning all relevant data. Intended for use in direct user access as opposed to developer scraping use, as well as easily exploring data.
Edited a typo on the README.md

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/devarsh1997/InfoMP

Made new changes.
removed useless folders added guinicorn in requirements.txt
MP csv containing names with urls of mp websites.
